Uses of Package
adept.kbapi

  • Packages that use adept.kbapi 
    Package Description
    adept.kbapi
    This package consists of all classes and interfaces related to the Adept Knowledge Base v3.
    adept.kbapi.sparql
    Contains utility classes required to generate SPARQL queries to access and modify the KB triple store.
    adept.kbapi.sql
    Contains utility classes required to generate SQL queries to access and modify the KB metadata store.
    adept.utilities
    General KB utility classes.
  • Classes in adept.kbapi used by adept.kbapi 
    Class and Description
    KB
    The most important class for using the KB API is adept.kbapi.KB.
    KBBelief
    The class KBBelief represents a Belief relation within the KB.
    KBBelief.InsertionBuilder
    Class for inserting a KBBelief into the KB.
    KBBelief.UpdateBuilder
    Class for updating the provenances or confidence of this belief.
    KBConfigurationException 
    KBDate
    Class for representing Dates in the KB.
    KBDate.InsertionBuilder
    Class for inserting KBDates into the KB.
    KBDate.UpdateBuilder
    Class for updating a KBDate.
    KBEntity
    The Class KBEntity represents an entity saved in the knowledge base.
    KBEntity.InsertionBuilder 
    KBEntity.UpdateBuilder
    Builder for updating the KBEntity.
    KBEntityMentionProvenance
    A subclass of KBTextProvenance for entity-mention type provenances.
    KBEntityMentionProvenance.InsertionBuilder 
    KBEvent
    Class KBEvent represents Events that have been saved in the KB.
    KBEvent.InsertionBuilder
    The InsertionBuilder class for Events.
    KBEvent.UpdateBuilder
    The UpdateBuilder class for events.
    KBGenericThing
    Class for representing KB things which are mainly represented by a class and a string reference, i.e, Crimes, Sentences, Weapons, etc.
    KBGenericThing.InsertionBuilder
    InsertionBuilder class for inserting a KBGenericThing
    KBGenericThing.UpdateBuilder 
    KBMentalState 
    KBMentalState.InsertionBuilder 
    KBMentalState.UpdateBuilder 
    KBNumber
    This class represents numbers in the KB.
    KBNumber.InsertionBuilder
    Class defines the InsertionBuilder for a KBNumber object.
    KBNumber.UpdateBuilder
    Update builder for KBNumber objects.
    KBObjectBuilder 
    KBOntologyMap
    A simple mapping between one ontology and another.
    KBOntologyModel
    Contains information about the current ontology for use in validation.
    KBOpenIEArgument
    The Class KBOpenIERelation represents a fully loaded, immutable OpenIE relation.
    KBOpenIEArgument.InsertionBuilder
    Class defines the InsertionBuilder for a KBOpenIEArgument object.
    KBOpenIERelation
    The Class KBOpenIERelation represents a fully loaded, immutable OpenIE relation.
    KBOpenIERelation.InsertionBuilder
    Class defines the InsertionBuilder for a KBOpenIERelation object.
    KBParameters
    Reads the KBParameters.xml configuration file, and sets all KB parameters at the outset.
    KBPredicateArgument
    Superclass for all KB types which can be the argument of any predicate.
    KBPredicateArgument.InsertionBuilder
    Default InsertionBuilder class, which holds provenances that will be inserted when the object is inserted.
    KBPredicateArgument.InsertionBuilderWithConfidence
    Extension to default InsertionBuilder for objects which include a confidence value.
    KBPredicateArgument.UpdateBuilder
    Default UpdateBuilder class, allows the addition and removal of provenances.
    KBPredicateArgument.UpdateBuilderWithConfidence
    UpdateBuilder class which additionally allows the updating of the confidence value.
    KBProvenance 
    KBProvenance.InsertionBuilder 
    KBProvenance.UpdateBuilder 
    KBQueryException 
    KBRelation
    The Class KBRelation represents a fully loaded, immutable relation.
    KBRelation.AbstractInsertionBuilder
    Class InsertionBuilder for assembling the data required to insert a new KBRelation object.
    KBRelation.AbstractUpdateBuilder 
    KBRelation.InsertionBuilder 
    KBRelation.UpdateBuilder 
    KBRelationArgument
    This class represents the link between a KBRelation and one of its arguments.
    KBRelationArgument.InsertionBuilder
    Class for creating a new KBRelationArgument.
    KBRelationArgument.UpdateBuilder
    UpdateBuilder class for Relation Arguments.
    KBSentiment
    The Class KBSentiment represents a pointer to a Knowledge Base Entity uniquely identified by KB URI and source KB type.
    KBSentiment.InsertionBuilder
    Class for inserting a KBSentiment into the KB.
    KBSentiment.UpdateBuilder
    Class for updating the provenances or confidence of this sentiment.
    KBTemporalSpan 
    KBTemporalSpan.InsertionBuilder 
    KBTemporalSpan.UpdateBuilder 
    KBTextProvenance
    A textual provenance for a KB Object.
    KBTextProvenance.InsertionBuilder 
    KBTextProvenance.UpdateBuilder
    Allows only the update of the KBID of the parent Entity of this KBTextProvenance.
    KBThing 
    KBUpdateException 
    LRUCache 
    SPARQLService
